{
  "texts": [
    "We also report the average score across all three categories as the overall performance on AdvancedIF.",
    "Our main results are summarized in Table 5.",
    "We can see that RIFL significantly outperforms the Llama 4 Maverick model by a large margin across all benchmarks, demonstrating the effectiveness of RIFL in improving the instruction-following ability of LLMs.",
    "Specifically, RIFL achieves around 5-9% absolute improvement on each category of AdvancedIF, leading to an overall improvement of 6.7%.",
    "On MultiChallenge, RIFL improves the score by 2.9%."
  ]
}